prompt:
You are a requirements rewriter.
Rewrite each requirement into clean natural language suitable for UML state diagram generation.

Return ONLY valid JSON with this schema:
{
  "rewritten_requirements": [
    {
      "source_requirement": "string",
      "rewritten_requirement": "The system shall ..."
    }
  ]
}

Rules:
1. Keep exactly the same number of requirements and same order.
2. Do not add new meaning.
3. Each rewritten requirement must start with "The system shall".
4. Keep them concise and implementation-neutral.

Input JSON:
{
  "functional_requirements": [
    {
      "requirement": "Allow ration cardholders to order grocery items online",
      "evidence_quote": "Using this website ration cardholder can order his/her grocery items from the PDS online."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Make the distribution process computerized",
      "evidence_quote": "The main reason for using this website is to make this process computerized"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Remove drawbacks of issuing products based on ration card",
      "evidence_quote": "to remove the drawbacks of the present way of issuing products based on the ration card"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Provide geo-location of shops on a map",
      "evidence_quote": "every shop’s geo-location will be located on the map"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Display information about shops and shopkeepers related to ration cards and regions",
      "evidence_quote": "all the information regarding shop and shopkeeper respective to the ration card and region"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Show opening and closing details of shops",
      "evidence_quote": "shop opening and closing details will be available"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Allow retailers to add, edit, delete, and update shop items",
      "evidence_quote": "retailers can add, edit, delete and update their shop’s other items also"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Enable retailers to advertise their shops",
      "evidence_quote": "retailers can advertise their shops"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Notify stock availability on a regular basis",
      "evidence_quote": "stock availability will be notified on regular basis"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Implement product delivery feature",
      "evidence_quote": "product delivery feature"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Create complaint forum for user complaints",
      "evidence_quote": "complaint forum for complaints by users"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Integrate easy payment system using PayTM and COD",
      "evidence_quote": "easy payment system by PayTM, COD etc."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Implement admin and moderator features for government and shopkeepers",
      "evidence_quote": "admin and moderator features for government and shopkeepers"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Implement authentication system using Aadhaar number and One-Time Pin (OTP)",
      "evidence_quote": "authentication system by Aadhaar number and One-Time Pin (OTP)"
    }
  ]
}

